# Vue 3 and Composition API

- Use composition API and declarative patterns; avoid options API.
- Use `<script setup>` for component definitions; type props and emits with defineProps<T>() and defineEmits.
- Use ref, reactive, and computed for reactive state.
- Use provide/inject when appropriate; implement custom composables for reusable logic.
